{"tid":2076538,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"身為P牌制度嘅推手，我想問可唔可以推行甩P制","createTime":"2020-06-23T14:52:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-27T01:48:11.000Z","uid":267881,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e73ed68587f74319093143ba12f4f72885f92c7d","tid":2076538,"uid":267881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T14:52:16.000Z","msg":"當日620連登發起眾籌全球登報令連登係政治舞台上聲名大燥，大量中共acc湧入，所以叫連仔阻截，分隔新舊會員<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1257985\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1257985</a><br />\n<br />\n但同時亦有壞處，好多因抗爭先加入連登嘅手足呢一年都出心出力，出咗好多重要post，奈何推唔到上頂，令其他會員錯失左重要資訊，同埋post量限制，有時見到手足想講重要嘢，又唔夠quota，舊會員就一日開十個膠post洗走晒重要post，好心痛<br />\n<br />\n所以我想拋磚，睇吓有冇可能改良P牌制<br />\n<br />\n方法一：只要係時事台/ 政事台曾經攞過1000+正皮又冇攞過1000+負皮嘅P牌仔可以申請甩P，如果之後出現1000+負皮就變返P<br />\n<br />\n方法二：admin積極大規模清洗五毛acc，之後增加P牌仔權限<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"791fe01041622af3eff747d66d5fe08ca2ea589a","tid":2076538,"uid":307203,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T14:52:28.000Z","msg":"是日電台<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【再推】La La Land改編革命歌！一齊將時代革命打入荷里活<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2076506\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2076506</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"06eb943349d57d99d6f69e15449f716b1ebc75ab","tid":2076538,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T14:52:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1344a980380b3d64a6f88d42febdf